org.wso2.transport.http.netty.sender.http2

Class Http2ClientChannel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wso2.transport.http.netty.sender.http2.Http2ClientChannel

  • public class Http2ClientChannel
extends Object
    Http2ClientChannel encapsulates the Channel associated with a particular connection.

    This shouldn't have anything related to a single message.
